<A>__{as the music continues bob, lyn and bill appear leading a column of nervous iraqi prisoners out of the building, towards the gates. lyn and bill are holding baby goats in their arms. a tripping bob is holding bunches of flowers it's as close as they can get to the illustration from the new earth army manual. lyn holds up a hand to stop the procession. larry stands in front of them, a gun in his hand, his face blank. lyn and larry stare at each other. then, unexpectedly, larry starts to cry.}
